prng.utility

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • prng.utility.Config
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>

    public class Config
extends Object
implements Iterable<String>
    Configuration data. The configuration is stored in a properties file. Different sections of the configuration file are distinguished by different prefixes on the property names.
    Author:
    Simon Greatrix
